@startuml
title Facade - Ejemplo 2 - solucion para arranque de aplicacion
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class ApplicationFacade {
    +start(): void
  }
  class ConfigurationLoader {
    +load(): void
  }
  class Database {
    +connect(): void
  }
  class Logger {
    +start(): void
  }
}

ApplicationFacade ..> Database : crea
ApplicationFacade ..> ConfigurationLoader : crea
ApplicationFacade ..> Logger : crea
ConfigurationLoader ..> Database : crea
ConfigurationLoader ..> Logger : crea
Logger ..> Database : crea
Main ..> ApplicationFacade : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
